Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.96,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, there was a man who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:11.94,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The story was interrupted and along with his heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:14.44,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,the prince lost his kindness towards people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:17.61,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and even his memories of having fought bravely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:21.58,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,And scattered throughout the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:25.92,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,the shards of the prince's heart\Nsought places to settle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.91,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and found their way into the people's\Nhearts who had voids in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:33.33,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Among those who were possessed by the shards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:37.23,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,were some who ended up making their own tales go awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:31.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've really and truly become Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:32.14,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,''The Princess's Vow''
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tuck your chin in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:35.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.87,0:02:42.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't even do that, you'll never\Nget out of the probationary class!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:48.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru isn't capable of doing two\Nthings at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She just has to walk with a book on her head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:52.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's something so easy, if she\Ncan't do it, she simply can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she'll never be able to become a prima ballerina!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she won't! There's no way Ahiru could\Npossibly become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say any more terrible things!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how hurt she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile! Smile for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:10.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But after getting dropped to the probationary class, isn't\NAhiru acting weird, being all goofy smiley since morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:13.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking more than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:15.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:20.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that anything happened, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So something DID happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:27.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:33.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, oh, yeah... a dream, it's about a dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:39.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this really strong and handsome prince,\Nbut this prince is fighting against an evil raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:42.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He can seal the raven away if\Nhe shatters his own heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:45.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,but when he loses his heart, he\Nalso loses his emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:49.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And this prince's eyes always look so\Nlonely, and for this prince, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:49.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a story like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:54.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Story?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:56.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's straight out of ''The Prince and the Raven''.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, it's this book, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:04.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The prince was a hero, who fought\Nagainst the demonic raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when they were inside\Nthe story that I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.69,0:04:09.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what's the name of the person\Nwho wrote this story?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:12.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's Drosselmeyer. That's\Ncommon knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:18.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be reading books like\Nthis and grinning like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Two books would be impossible for you, Ahiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:23.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you can do it by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck. You've got nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:30.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so like, does Drosselmeyer-san\Nlive in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He died ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:39.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The story ends part way through too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:43.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. I think he died while writing the book, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:46.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he came out of the story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,and lost his heart in order\Nto seal away the raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:56.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the person who was writing the story\Ndied and the characters in the story came out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:03.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it isn't as strange as a\Nduck turning into a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:07.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Mytho-senpai is a prince out of a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he's so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.59,0:05:13.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:16.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Rue-chan knows about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:18.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mytho-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's going on a picnic with Rue-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:27.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I'm just a duck...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll practice or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:31.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Mytho around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter with Mytho-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:39.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He went out without telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that? He's Rue-chan's boyfriend after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's with Rue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:45.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:48.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:49.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:51.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:57.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he knows about Mytho-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:01.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you know the story ''The Prince and the Raven''?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:03.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:08.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a childish tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah, acting so high and mighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And he doesn't even have a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:22.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho-senpai is a prince from inside a story,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:24.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm the only one who knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:28.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect my prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing hooky. I'm just taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:35.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed to do that. Besides, if I\Nsee Mytho-senpai and Rue-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell them that nasty guy\Nwas looking for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:44.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is a shy little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you approach it, it will hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:47.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Edel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is a lonesome little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move away from it, it will give chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having doubts about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:01.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, there's this person and there's another\Nperson who's good friends with that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that person also has another good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that person's friends aren't friends with one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind makes flames burn and the treetops sway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But flames burn trees to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, wind and flames and trees, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean they can never get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:28.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the wind's too strong, it would put out\Nthe fire and topple the trees too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:30.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:32.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But thank you, Edel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're going on a picnic, maybe\Nthey'll be at the park over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:48.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:52.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:53.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me that you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! Should I go back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I should go back, shouldn't l?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:04.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Rue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:23.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some water. Get it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do?! He'll see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:37.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they really are perfect for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:40.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But they didn't look like they were having much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If he were to say something like that to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I really love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:04.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My-My-Mytho-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:10.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Um, since the weather's so nice today, it's bright\Nduring the day, but I'm sure it'll be dark at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid me, what am I doing stating the obvious?!\NI have to say something funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:19.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I love taking walks! And you love Rue-chan, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what the heck am I saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:22.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:24.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Probably?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:31.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what the feeling of love is, but Rue and\NFakir are the only ones who'll tell me what to do, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Mytho is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:41.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mytho-senpai! I mean, Mytho! Your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:42.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you making that weird face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a weird face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir and Rue don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:01.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the prince's eyes. The poor prince who lost his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:06.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he doesn't know his own feelings,\Nnot even about loving or hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:15.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular, but rather, I want to work\Nsuper hard on all sorts of things and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! That injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get worse if you don't wash it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, it's not that serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The water that you went and got!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:32.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm really sorry! I'll...I'll um, go get more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:36.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that, river water probably wouldn't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rue-chan should have good tasting water, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The water I could get from a house\Naround here wouldn't work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:44.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I get it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I'm not in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:47.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I walk too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My-Mytho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'll go get the water, so just wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, where can I get water?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Water from a restaurant would be perfect, wouldn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:06.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Open?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's the restaurant's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:15.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, this is a restaurant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is! Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,One moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:32.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! I am the owner and chef, Ebine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:32.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find out about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear it from a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then did you go out of your way to find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:39.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it was by pure chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:46.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is splendid! I've never had a customer like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please, sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, I'm not a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:54.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I came for some water...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:57.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... water?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:00.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:03.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please have a meal while you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But I don't have any money...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:10.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, I had some shrimp paté.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The pendant just glowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But does that mean she has one of the shards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Mytho go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:42.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take Mytho out without letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho doesn't belong to you, now does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't belong to you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho mentioned ''feeling''.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:54.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Mytho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:58.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to get some water and hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:12:59.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,By himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else would he be going with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:05.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you at all. What are you so frantic about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:08.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to look for Mytho, aren't you? I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please help yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, but we...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, this is far from enough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to check to see if she has a heart shard or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So is this! And this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:32.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they all cold? And there's not\Nmuch taste to them either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And they LOOK so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's rainbow trout meunière!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This one looks warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, rabbit cream stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:46.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is piping hot dumpling salad!\NFurthermore, grilled pork shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all cold! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:54.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, don't you think something's strange here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like why are all the dishes cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:00.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or like why is she feeding us for free?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:07.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Mytho doesn't even understand how\Nit feels when something's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:10.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That concludes Course A!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is Course B!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:12.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:17.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hey, I'm going to the restroom for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, I better hurry up and check!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:31.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first customers in a long time. They're eating so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:34.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to have them eat even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which will taste better compared to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Which will taste better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:44.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A... gra...ve...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:56.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I don't care what happens to me, but Mytho...\NI have to at least protect Mytho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a story that goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:02.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A brother and sister wandering in the forest\Ncome across a gingerbread house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:06.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a kind old woman appears and\Nserves them some food,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:10.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,but she was really planning to fatten up the brother\Nand sister, and to eat them afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:15.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! Mytho doesn't understand that he's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get out of here while we...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Owow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:25.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Recipes? And a photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:27.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:31.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, uh, uh, um, I was\Nthinking of going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:35.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The food hasn't been eaten yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:37.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who hasn't eaten what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,More must be eaten! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who hasn't eaten what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go back until the food's been eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already full!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll still eat more, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:55.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Open this door! Please open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to eat, you can go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:03.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she locked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:08.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, it's going awry. The story's going awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:12.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart shards make their way into the void in people's hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,and make their stories go awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:18.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears a heart that is too pure is a heavy burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:24.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how will you handle this story, Princess Tutu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The little nuisance is gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:43.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to keep eating more and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:52.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mealtime is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest a while, my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give back my customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:09.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance with me, Ebine-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:13.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dancing isn't for me... my job is to cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:16.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And to have my customers eat my cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:20.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do by having him keep eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:23.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have him eat more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:28.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I just want him to eat lots and lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my precious customer to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:36.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because having your fill of delicious food is happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:37.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I'd find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:41.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This person's heart isn't where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:44.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't let him go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What feeling is that shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:56.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want him to enjoy my cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:58.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a restaurant is for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:03.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is your cooking so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:08.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you force him to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you imprison him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:15.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what it is that you're feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:17.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:21.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance with me, Ebine-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:26.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:31.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt just a little uncertainty, but the rest of it was all\Nbliss and I could have burst with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:36.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A nice atmosphere. I had happy\Nconversations. Delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:40.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful restaurant. A wonderful couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:44.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I would cook and ask, ''I wonder which\Nwill taste better compared to you?''
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:49.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He would always tease me and say, ''Yours\Nstill has a long way to go.''
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:50.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was happiness for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which will taste better compared to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:56.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what those words meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one left to tease me when I ask about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:06.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the recipes that he wrote down, but the\Nperson who cooked them is no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:13.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I wanted to at least have my\Ncustomers stay as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the feeling of loneliness, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:25.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but this isn't where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go! I'll be all alone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:39.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You're not alone, Ebine-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:44.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you have the recipes left\Nto you by the one you loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:48.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of dishes are waiting, wanting to be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:53.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A gift left to you by the one you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:56.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The power to turn loneliness into strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:04.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:09.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I can cook warm dishes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Warm, just like your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:15.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make this into a wonderful restaurant again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me, my Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:29.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My prince, your feelings belong within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:32.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life belongs within your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:39.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:55.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:20:59.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho, what are you doing in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:03.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:05.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:07.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Tutu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he knows it's me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:15.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She touched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:16.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Tutu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous. That's just a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:19.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:22.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu is... part of the story too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a duck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:33.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's blessed with beauty, cleverness, and strength,but the\Nthing is, the princess is fated never to be with her prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:37.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment she confesses her love, she\Nturns into a speck of light and vanishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:38.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:40.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's part of the story? And what's real?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu is me and I'm a duck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:44.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tutu is... Tutu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:48.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Princess Tutu is a tragic princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:52.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stories aren't always guaranteed a happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:28.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,All I want to do is to restore Mytho's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not thinking about being with him or\Nconfessing to him or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:34.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what this emotion is that I'm feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:36.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You better not be the one making\NMytho remember weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:39.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's Princess Tutu from the fairy tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:40.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The story will become real.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:43.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In this town, where reality and stories intermingle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.37,0:23:45.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:48.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fated never to be with the one I love, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:51.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,All you children who love stories,\Ncome gather around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:55.19,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,''Giselle''
